"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640317815,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"iV05jGnDk2DZ7wdZASGTlHT2Ossl3pRr6LGw9GmN6WI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x00B3f08a56A2AFA92372Bc225aF184D2A2506f96\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"zmT7WeJsgHvTZCRQM2OdTgTxH87BNNZDdYkQ6BwlVeA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"fAxh9dHKVVViubMSzP4Tya4LOEm-SpwLxTXC44xXXzo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"_qXQxFil-c7zPa_vlp1tIJXFnMnQIyQwRNUCP5F0yYNfjf9JN4SDUAkfMpa-VtY_1Zgpd42KaJs0STc6DN6AXQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x775b8b65ba5f0c3acf2536d20f2631ca33d18ffdf2ddf16160acfbbd4eafc85c5ca337477984979db292dabb6b03c72e7c77b0a77c36da4b91feacf511913e0b1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"zmT7WeJsgHvTZCRQM2OdTgTxH87BNNZDdYkQ6BwlVeA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"fAxh9dHKVVViubMSzP4Tya4LOEm-SpwLxTXC44xXXzo\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi